ŠFrom Phil to Alina, my wife and love of my life.
For memories of lunches and moments shared
in Berkeley Square Mayfair and in
the London Town that we grew to love together
and call our home."╚
┼[LEFT]
Angel
Occasionally, we are graced with the presence of an
earth bound angel. They are unable to stay with us for
long, but while they do, they bring unexpected joy
and happiness to all they touch.

[RIGHT]
Eva
07-10-2001  ~ 07-12-2003
Chasing pigeons, feeding ducks, in spite of illness 
living every moment"╩
ŪPresented by the London Bloomsbury LPC Class of 2017
In Memory of Johan Garcia
19th December 1991 to 11th June 2018
A loving son, a genuine friend to us all. Above all else a fantastic human being"ą
═In memory of Bruno lImerini MBE
April 1933 - February 2019
In 1990 Bruno raised ┬Ż120,000 for the Gardens to be landscaped to their current design
He then organised annual festivals in the improved Gardens"ų
